{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B1\n    \n      Smart onboarding tour · 3 persona variants\n      First visit. Welcome card asks \"Are you here to (a) Learn from scratch, (b) Brush up for interviews, (c) Just explore?\". Each answer runs a different 90-second tour highlighting relevant modes.\n      \n        👋 Welcome.\n        What brings you here today?\n        \n          \n            📖\n            Learning from scratch\n            tour Learn + Review\n          \n          \n            ⏱️\n            Interview prep\n            tour Drill + AI scoring\n          \n          \n            🎨\n            Just exploring\n            tour Build + tools\n          \n        \n        or skip tour","choice":"b1","id":null,"timestamp":1776666998475}
{"source":"user-event","type":"click","text":"B2\n    \n      Inline find · ⌘F works in lessons\n      Most sites break ⌘F inside scrollable lesson columns. Architex catches ⌘F, opens an inline search box, highlights matches in yellow, cycles with Enter.\n      \n        \n          🔍\n          instance\n          3 of 7\n          ↑ ↓\n        \n        A Singleton has only one instance. The static method returns the cached instance on subsequent calls. If no instance exists, create one.","choice":"b2","id":null,"timestamp":1776667005500}
